  "instructions": [
    "In a small pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the caraway seeds and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the scallions and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the sour cream and grated Jarlsberg cheese until smooth.",
    "In a separate bowl, combine the full-fat yogurt and ferment-kimchi.",
    "Spoon the yogurt mixture into a slate tile vessel.",
    "Top with the caraway-seed scallion mixture and a sprinkle of salt and pepper.",
    "Serve immediately."
